product description: Introducing the ultimate laptop backpack designed for maximum safety and comfort. Made with durable, water-resistant materials, this backpack keeps your laptop protected from the elements and accidental spills. The padded laptop compartment fits most laptops up to 17 inches, and is specially designed with shock-absorbing foam to keep your device secure and safe from bumps and drops. The backpack also features padded shoulder straps and a padded back panel for added comfort during long commutes or trips. The adjustable shoulder strap helps to distribute the weight evenly across your body, reducing strain on your shoulders and back. In addition to the laptop compartment, the backpack has plenty of room for all of your other essentials, including books, documents, and personal items. The organizer pockets and key clip keep your items organized and easily accessible. Whether you're commuting to work or hitting the trails, this laptop backpack is the perfect choice for keeping your device safe and secure, while also providing maximum comfort on the go. So, it is an ideal choice for people who are looking for a laptop backpack that is both safe and comfortable.

This unisex travelling bag is designed for trekking, hiking, and camping, with a premium padded shoulder strap and mesh padding for maximum comfort. The padded back panel ensures breathability during extended wear. This backpack features a premium buckle and YKK zipper for added durability, making it the perfect mountain bag or camping rucksack. The front opening provides easy access to your gear, and the integrated rain cover keeps your belongings dry during inclement weather. This large backpack is suitable for men, women, boys, and girls, and can be used as a biker backpack or riding backpack. It has a Luggage/suitcase-type opening, which makes packing and unpacking a breeze. The back padding ensures that it's comfortable to wear for long periods of time, making it perfect for touring or flight travel. The TRAWOC backpack is perfect for daypack use, with excess storage capacity and weight-bearing capacity too. It's available in a variety of colors and sizes, making it suitable for any adventure or occasion. The 1-year warranty ensures that you'll be able to enjoy your backpack for years to come. Whether you're a tourist, tourister, or outdoor enthusiast, this big bag is perfect for you. It's a must-have for anyone who loves adventure and wants to travel in style and comfort. So, get your TRAWOC backpack today and start your next adventure!

product description: Decent BACKPACK: The Tabelito Backpack / Daypack is made of HIGH QUALITY Anti Scratch Fabric with a sturdy zipper design, making it incredibly sturdy, tear-resistant, and capable of protecting your items from dust, rain, and filth. Even more robust and long-lasting are the strong buckle and zipper. LARGE CAPACITY & MULTI COMPARTMENTS & LIGHT WEIGHT: The backpack has three compartments. There is ample storage for clothes, books, a lunchbox, daily needs, and tech equipment accessories in the separate laptop compartment that fits a 15.6-inch laptop as well as a 15-inch, 14-inch, and 13-inch or Mac book. The middle compartment has enough capacity for a laptop charger, an iPad, a tablet, a smartphone, a document file, and other necessary accessories. There are two small elastic mesh side pockets for water bottles and a front compartment with zipper pockets for easy access items like a mask, wallet, metro card, and wallet. Make your goods more accessible and organised. HIGH QUALITY MATERIAL: The metal zippers on our backpack are made of high-quality, water-resistant Polyester fabric. Lightweight and strong build guarantee daily use that is safe and durable. Perfect for shopping, office work, business travel, weekend trips, and other outdoor activities. It is also the ideal backpack for teens, boys, girls, adults, and other genders.

product description: Padded laptop sleeve compatible upto 17" size. Elasticated strap keeps laptop in place. Padded carry handle for firm yet comfortable grip to carry over long periods. Front easy access multi level organizer to keep knick-knacks organised. Lightweight, durable, water-resistant proudly “made in india” fabrics. 200 denier poly lining material in compartment separators. 300 denier poly oxford fabric for main body. 400 denier dobby hard-wearing fabric at bottom for minimal wear and tear. All fabrics water-resistant upto 80 min of 500 mm rainfall. N-toxic bpa free zipper. World’s best ykk assurance of smooth running and durable runner.Tested to 500 opening /closing cycles. Tensile strength holding upto 83 kg. Elasticated full fabric bottle/umbrella holder on both sides. No risk of tearing/cutting unlike mesh pockets. 8mm thick cushioning and fully ventilated padded back support for long term carrying comfort.Full 0.5 mm hdpe support in back provided stability and strength. ‘s’ shaped triple-layered triple-density foam padded shoulder strap, fully adjustable for customised fit depending on your height and contents in bag. All buckles of virgin hdpe proudly “made in india” . Easy to adjust bag with just a flick of the finger whatever be the weight tensile breakage strength tested to 65 kgs. 3-ply 210 denier 100% polyster thread used all across tensile breakage strength tested to 4 kg

product description: At American Tourister, we believe travel should be fun. We take pride in making stylish, high quality, and yeah, fun backpacks that you can rely on. Marking our presence in 100+ countries making it the most preferred luggage brand worldwide. This lightweight & voluminous backpack comes with multiple compartments that make it perfect for your college/office/school or outdoor travel. This backpack made of durable polyester fabric, is equipped with large compartments to hold enough notebooks, textbooks & journals for your college.The backpack has an internal organizer that provides easy access to your phone charger, stationery or whatever you need on the go and still has ample space left for your headphones, your personal diary or the novel you're currently hooked on to. This backpack also has a front stash compartment big enough to accommodate your essentials like phone, power bank, wallet, etc. It has padded mesh back & shoulder straps with breathable system for better back support. It comes with pockets on the side to comfortably accommodate your bottle or umbrella for convenience of access. Each backpack passes a series of rigorous global quality tests.

product description: Decent BACKPACK: The Tabelito Backpack / Daypack is made of HIGH QUALITY Anti Scratch Fabric with a sturdy zipper design, making it incredibly sturdy, tear-resistant, and capable of protecting your items from dust, rain, and filth. Even more robust and long-lasting are the strong buckle and zipper. LARGE CAPACITY & MULTI COMPARTMENTS & LIGHT WEIGHT: The backpack has three compartments. There is ample storage for clothes, books, a lunchbox, daily needs, and tech equipment accessories in the separate laptop compartment that fits a 15.6-inch laptop as well as a 15-inch, 14-inch, and 13-inch or Mac book. The middle compartment has enough capacity for a laptop charger, an iPad, a tablet, a smartphone, a document file, and other necessary accessories. There are two small elastic mesh side pockets for water bottles and a front compartment with zipper pockets for easy access items like a mask, wallet, metro card, and wallet. Make your goods more accessible and organised. HIGH QUALITY MATERIAL: The metal zippers on our backpack are made of high-quality, water-resistant Polyester fabric. Lightweight and strong build guarantee daily use that is safe and durable. Perfect for shopping, office work, business travel, weekend trips, and other outdoor activities. It is also the ideal backpack for teens, boys, girls, adults, and other genders.

This durable, modern travel case offers secure storage with a spacious, fully-lined interior and multiple zippered pockets for stashing smaller items and valuables. Take off for one night travel light for business with this convenient rolling suitcase. Pack clothing, essentials, and devices neatly and easily, and feel secure as you set off on your next adventure. Featuring four multi-directional double or single spinner wheels, traveling with the Tommy Hilfiger is a smooth, user-friendly experience. With fluid, 360-degree turning capabilities, rushing to catch your flight while being slowed down by cumbersome luggage will be a thing of the past. Turn corners and navigate tight spaces effortlessly with this agile rolling suitcase, and enjoy a stress-free trip. Tommy Hilfiger travel luggage also features a telescopic trolley with a top and side handle and handy push-button mechanism for easy lifting.

product description: This durable and lightweight backpack from Fur Jaden can keep you sorted throughout the day while also being super stylish, thus making it the perfect modern and functional accessory for any user – male or female. This backpack can be the perfect complement to your bold and charismatic persona, while its multiple inner chambers can hold all your stuff with convenience. Fur Jaden backpacks are young, vibrant and fashionable accessories which are also a symbol of sophistication. This backpack is high on aesthetics as well as on utility and functionality. This unisex backpack from Fur Jaden comes in an anti-theft design which lets you carry your laptop anywhere with confidence. Keep your belongings secure as your score high on the style quotient with this functional backpack. One of the most striking features of this backpack is that it allows you to charge your phone while you are travelling. The charging dock which comes attached to the backpack allows you to connect your portable charger seamlessly for maximum convenience.The material of this backpack from Fur Jaden is water resistant, which keeps any worries about getting it wet in the rain or accidental splashes at bay. Your laptop and every other belonging will stay safe from water as long as you keep them inside your backpack. This backpack from Fur Jaden comes with substantial capacity to accommodate your laptop and other goods with ease. The large capacity of this backpack can store laptops up to a 15.6 inches without any hassle. Weighing in at only 0.7kg, this Fur Jaden backpack with anti-theft feature is a breeze to carry around. Most of the weight you will feel is that of the goods you carry inside, as the backpack does not impose much weight on the user. This multipurpose and water resistant backpack from Fur Jaden can take you from day to night, thanks to its multiple compartments. With 1 main compartment and 7 small, inner pockets, it lets you store all your belongings and keeps them sorted too. Pattern: Solid.

product description: Stay organized all day with a durable and lightweight backpack from Fur Jaden. This back pack is a stylish and functional accessory for men and women. Can add admiration to an appealing and daring personality with a remarkable aesthetics and functionality. This backpack features an anti-theft design. You can also charge your phone on the go and organize your stuff like pro. Fur Jaden functional back pack is apt to protect your gadgets and belongings from being stolen while you travel, thanks to its special anti-theft design. Now keep your belongings safe with style. The backpack features multiple compartments that you may use for your laptop and other essentials. A remarkable feature of this backpack allows you to charge your phone while you are on the move. With an attached charging dock in the back you may connect a portable power bank with ease. Weighing about 600grams, this backpack is lightweight. The backpack is able to house a laptop of up to 15.6 inches and has seven inner compartments to place your other essentials. Made from durable quality polymer this Fur Jaden back pack is sturdy and reliable. Flaunt this bag with style and low maintenance as this bag is washable. This backpack is also suitable for school or college. The straps are designed to distribute the weight equally on each shoulder preventing any sort of discomfort. Use this back pack for office, college/school or during travels.
